bilingual.target: 没有多样性，我们的星球无法生存。

bilingual.source: The deer are being trained to survive outside the park.
bilingual.target: 这些鹿正在接受训练以在公园外生存。

bilingual.source: Stephen Hawking believed humans must move into space to survive.
bilingual.target: 斯蒂芬·霍金认为人类必须进入太空才能生存。

bilingual.source: Then I'll be able to survive even when the tall buildings are flooded.
bilingual.target: 那样即使高楼被淹我也能生存。

bilingual.source: She felt love for the first time, but a creature of snow could not survive such a warm heart.
bilingual.target: 她第一次感受到了爱，但一个雪的生物无法在如此温暖的心中生存。

bilingual.source: The more we know about this lovely creature, the greater the chance it will survive and keep its place in the natural world for a long time to come.
bilingual.target: 我们对这种可爱的生物了解得越多，它生存并在自然界中长期存在的机会就越大。
植物需要空气才能生存。
他们不得不乞讨才能生存。
人类需要氧气才能生存。

list.abstract: SURVIVE 结合了欧美的图案设计风格以及亚洲的设计版型，为消费者打造最为贴身的时尚潮流服饰，产品种类包括： TEE、POLO、外套、夹克、针织衫、帽衫、斗篷、打底裤、牛仔裤等覆盖多个品类。
survive是一个英语单词，可以用作动词，可以翻译为幸存、活下来，等等。

yingyinNormal.en: Only the paranoid survive, right, Finch?
yingyinNormal.zh: 只有偏执狂才能生存，是吧，芬奇？

yingyinNormal.en: If she wants to survive, she has to follow our rules.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是她想生存，必须守我们的规矩。

yingyinNormal.en: We no longer serve you. We serve only us. May the fittest survive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不会再为你们服务。我们只为我们自己服务。适者生存。

yingyinNormal.en: And the only way it can survive and thrive is for each of you to claim your rightful place.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而它之所以能生存并发展，依靠你们每一个人各司其职。

yingyinNormal.en: She made the case that if we break down in the middle of nowhere, your Nebraska backwoods skills and brawny hands will give us the best chance to survive in the wild.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她提出，如果我们在前不着村后不着店的地方出故障，你在内布拉斯加边远地区的生存技能和健壮的大手能增加我们在野外生存的机会。

yingyinNormal.en: Here people they survive. They live to live, they don't live to get rich because here there is no supermarket.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里的人为生存而活，他们自给自足，不求荣华富贵，这里你找不到超市。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: To survive in these waters scarce in nutrients, coral shelters an alga within it which feeds by day on sunlight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了在这片营养匮乏的水域生存,珊瑚庇护着一种靠光合作用为生的藻类。

yingyinNormal.en: Well "Darwin" is already a nickname and you know it sort of fits. Adapt to survive and all. Check this out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯，“达尔文”已经是外号了，你看，还挺合适的，适者生存什么的，看看这个。

yingyinNormal.en: No. It's not their fault you abandoned them in the arena. They're doing and saying whatever they can to survive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不可能。你们把他们丢在那里又不是他们的错，他们做的和说的一切都是为了生存。

yingyinNormal.en: If you wish to survive, you need to cultivate a strong mental attitude. You've got to obey the rules. Pandora rules.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你想生存下来，就得养成钢铁般坚毅的精神，你必须遵守规则，潘多拉法则。

yingyinNormal.en: I know I'm supposed to hate humans, but there's something about them. They don't just survive. They discover, they create. I mean, just look at what they do with food.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道我要痛恨人类才对，但是他们有很迷人的东西，除了求生存他们同时发明和创造。看看他们处理食物就知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, that's too bad. I'll survive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真不幸。死不了的。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't. Okay. Here. If you survive, call me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不能。好吧，给你，要是你活下来，叫我。

yingyinNormal.en: The grasses had found a way to survive the crisis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 草类找到了应对危机的好办法。

yingyinNormal.en: A rather short siege that I didn't expect to survive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 快是快，我当时都没指望能活下来。

yingyinNormal.en: Survive. Bring peace between orcs and humans. You must.
yingyinNormal.zh: 活下去，为兽人与人类之间带来和平，你必须这样。

yingyinNormal.en: What do you want us to do? I want you to survive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想让我们做什么？我想让你们活下去。

yingyinNormal.en: Are they likely to survive, and so on. And are they?
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看那些庄园是否还能为继。他们能吗？

yingyinNormal.en: You'll survive. You all will. Live your lives while you can.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你会适应的，你们都会。抓紧时间享受生活吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Set your house in order, and dig in for the battle to survive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 安顿好你的船，准备打场持久战。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: During their six- to twelve-week voyage, they <highlight>survived</highlight> on barely enough food allotted to them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在长达六至十二周的航程中，他们靠分配给他们的勉强足够的食物生存。

examination_example.sentence: He has failed to understand that monarchies have largely <highlight>survived</highlight> because they provide a service—as non-controversial and non-political heads of state.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他未能理解君主制之所以能够继续存在，很大程度上是因为它们提供了一项服务——作为无争议和非政治性的国家元首。

examination_example.sentence: It becomes clear that we have an excellent chance of <highlight>surviving</highlight> for tens, if not hundreds, of thousands of years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 很明显，我们极有可能继续存在数万年，甚至几十万年。

examination_example.sentence: Many of the ships were lost in storms, many passengers died of disease, and infants rarely <highlight>survived</highlight> the journey.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多船只在风暴中失踪，许多乘客死于疾病，婴儿也很少在旅途中幸存下来。

examination_example.sentence: Scientific claims will <highlight>survive</highlight> challenges.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科学主张将经受住挑战。

examination_example.sentence: They are better able to <highlight>survive</highlight> or handle disease.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们能够更好地生存或处理疾病。

examination_example.sentence: Women are more capable of <highlight>surviving</highlight> or handling disease than men.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 女性比男性更有能力生存或应对疾病。

examination_example.sentence: We're served up an endless stream of advice on "how to <highlight>survive</highlight> your 40s".
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们源源不断地收到了关于“如何度过40多岁”的建议。

examination_example.sentence: According to the author, humans can hardly <highlight>survive</highlight> if separated from their community.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据作者的观点，如果离开了他们的社区，人类几乎无法生存。

examination_example.sentence: Preliminary inspections also suggested the three ornate (装饰华丽的) stained glass "rose" windows appeared to have <highlight>survived</highlight> the fire, officials said.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 官员们说，初步检查还表明，三扇华丽的彩色玻璃“玫瑰”窗似乎在火灾中幸存了下来。

examination_example.sentence: Few babies <highlight>survive</highlight> this rare condition, and those who do must endure numerous operations and are likely to have complex needs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 很少有婴儿能在这种罕见的情况下存活下来，存活下来的还必须经受多次手术，可能还有复杂的护理需求。

examination_example.sentence: As automation spreads further, the question is how these remote communities will <highlight>survive</highlight> when the old jobs are eliminated.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 随着自动化的进一步普及，问题是当旧的工作岗位被淘汰时，这些偏远的社区将如何生存。

examination_example.sentence: Four out of six birds that <highlight>survived</highlight> for at least five months overwinter on rubbish dumps in northern Morocco.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在摩洛哥北部，存活了至少五个月的鸟中，六分之四在垃圾堆上过冬。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 不过，一些勇敢的人幸存了下来，还有一些留在山洞里的人。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

n. 幸存者；生还者；剩余者；善于生存的人；存者

word_family.mean: v. 活下来；幸存；比…活得长；坚持下来

examination_example.sentence: However, the domestic dog's special place as "man's best friend" has allowed it to <highlight>survive</highlight> (存活) in a human world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，家养狗作为“人类最好的朋友”的特殊地位使它得以在人类世界中生存。

examination_example.sentence: Most people believe in the long run, there is no practical reason for newspapers to <highlight>survive</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大多数人认为，从长远来看，报纸没有留存下去的实际理由。

examination_example.sentence: Now I feel I could <highlight>survive</highlight> anywhere!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在我觉得我可以在任何地方生存！

sense_info_list.en: continue to live or exist in spite of

examination_example.sentence: For the baby girls who are lucky enough to <highlight>survive</highlight> (生存), their life may be still around "water", just like their mothers'.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于那些幸运存活下来的女婴来说，她们的生命可能还在“水”周围，就像她们的母亲一样。

examination_example.sentence: In the film Arctic, one man must <highlight>survive</highlight> in the icy landscape after his plane crashes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在电影《北极》中，一个人必须在飞机坠毁后在冰天雪地中生存下来。

examination_example.sentence: Because of the extreme temperatures in the desert, it is a very difficult place to <highlight>survive</highlight>(幸存).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由于沙漠的极端温度，这是一个很难生存的地方。
